  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Project Engineer (M&E)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Duties &amp; Responsibilities:-</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Overseeing the procurement of materials.</li>\n  <li>Coordinating with the various clients , consultants, main-contractors , architects, sub contractors and specialist to ensure the smooth and timely execution of the project deliverables.</li>\n  <li>Ensuring that all works are carried out in accordance with the project specifications.</li>\n  <li>Ensuring that all works are carried out within the project budget given.</li>\n  <li>Overseeing the various design elements of the project.</li>\n  <li>Providing timely submissions for cash flow and progress claims.</li>\n  <li>Procurement of materials and ensuring the timely delivery of the materials as per site requirement.</li>\n  <li>Ensuring that all team members can deliver their daily works and that the team meets the project requirements.</li>\n  <li>Monitoring and improving of overall project progress to meet critical milestone dates.</li>\n  <li>Submission of monthly / weekly progress and safety reports.</li>\n  <li>Reporting of all project matters to the management.</li>\n  <li>Preparing and presenting of consolidated contractual claims to the client representives.</li>\n  <li>Any other works/tasks given by the Management for the completion of the project and other Ad-hoc assignments.</li>\n</ul>",
